Being a teacher I have been
teaching my students to be

00:06:25.251 --> 00:06:28.453
to be very, very,
very cooperative

00:06:28.520 --> 00:06:31.424
and think about
universality.

00:06:31.490 --> 00:06:34.727
So that we can live
together peacefully.

