Just a little talk with your
average, you know, farmer.

00:06:38.998 --> 00:06:41.634
It happens a lot in
Pakistan and I love it.

00:06:41.701 --> 00:06:43.235
<i> But this is part
 of my, you know,</i>

00:06:43.302 --> 00:06:45.004
<i> excitement of being
 a photographer</i> .

